         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">13 December 1861 ¶ My dear Dr Mueller. ¶  ¶ The little water hen which you sent me this morning (and which I hope has safely reached you again) which flew on board the ship Clutha, ¶ Cluthahad arrived...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">61.12.13</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Frederick McCoy</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Director’s letterbooks, MVS 2/1 2, p. 18, Melbourne Museum.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.1666in; text-indent: -0.1666in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found; item is a file copy.</p>
               </note>13 December 1861</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Dr Mueller.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The little water hen which you sent me this morning (and which I hope has safely reached you again) which flew on board the ship Clutha,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.1666in; text-indent: -0.1666in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Clutha</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>had arrived from<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>London<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>on<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>30 September 1861 and,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>after discharging cargo at Hobson's Bay (Melbourne),<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>moved to Geelong on 14 October to load wool<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>before sailing for London<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>on 18<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>November 1861.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>is<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Porphyrio Martinica</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>a bird common in all the warmer parts of Central and South America and the West Indian Islands. It is<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>easily kept in confinement on bread rice<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>&amp;c and a little chopped meat occasionally</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Ever &amp;c</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>F. McC.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="Normal"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I enclose a form of account for the corals and sponges for which I must ask you to have the price entered if you would be so kind, as I could not fix it myself: they are neither rare nor very good, but we require examples from N. E. Australia such as Mr. Fitzalan's<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.1666in; text-indent: -0.1666in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Eugene Fitzalan had moved to Qld<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>from Geelong<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in 1860 and was a pioneer settler of Bowen in 1861; he had previusly collected for M in Tasmania<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>1854<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(Dowe and Nelson (2015), pp.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>800-01).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
